      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "You'd see the usual collection of broken things: men in ill-fitting, dark coats who look like they haven't seen a decent meal in weeks, their faces etched with a permanent kind of sour resignation. There are the sharp-eyed hustlers, always draped in cheap, flashy jewelry that catches the meager light, watching everyone with predatory patience. Then there are the silent ones, the ones who just lean against the walls, their presence a heavy, unspoken threat, blending into the grime like it's their natural habitat.",
